description:
How I made money as a part-time content creator:

- paid to post content on a new app 
- sponsored posts
- affiliate links
- paid article

Mar: $0 - just starting out, i received a few gifted and paid offers up to $150. I was just focused on learning + growing

Apr: $0 - started getting offers up to $400! said no to all of them, still just trying to grow

May: $55 (affiliate links lol) - average deal size grew to $600. I told myself anything less than $1000 wasn‚Äôt worth the hassle‚Ä¶

Jun: $1165 - OK so I went back on my goal of $1000 per post. I took a few smaller deals but i was excited for this milestone ü•≥!!! 

Jul: $2253 - still learning to pitch, negotiate, and know my worth but SOO grateful for where I‚Äôm at ü•π

My goals for the next few months:
- get into UGC üò´ I know I keep saying this but omg I promise soon
- start doing outreach‚Ä¶ 0 luck on apps so far and I haven‚Äôt sent out any emails/DMsü•∂

*NO CREATOR FUND BC IM IN CANADA ü•≤*
